{"tid":1306202,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"我要獨立調查會呀!!!!!","createTime":"2019-07-11T05:27:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T05:53:01.000Z","uid":278285,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f3a9030a44ab1616e83ef4c363ab897839407ae1","tid":1306202,"uid":278285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T05:27:31.000Z","msg":"sorry P牌 第一次出post<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我要獨立調查會呀!!!!!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/01觀點/347734/監警會-三無-獨立調查委員會必須成立\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F01%E8%A7%80%E9%BB%9E%2F347734%2F%E7%9B%A3%E8%AD%A6%E6%9C%83-%E4%B8%89%E7%84%A1-%E7%8D%A8%E7%AB%8B%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5%E5%A7%94%E5%93%A1%E6%9C%83%E5%BF%85%E9%A0%88%E6%88%90%E7%AB%8B&d=i5E3ds%2FeSPFE00WLmt852wmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=c8061ee1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/01觀點/347734/監警會-三無-獨立調查委員會必須成立</a><br />\n<br />\n由611 612 已經見住班撕紙狗愈來愈倡狂 再到旺角遊行嗰日 又叫人隻揪 又兇班記者哥哥姐姐 全部都未打瘋狗症針呀佢地 痴線架 <br />\n而我地普通市民就連投訴都冇number 咩都做唔到 <br />\n係呀你可以起狗底呀 洩憤呀 之後呢?? 等比人拉? 洩完憤咪又係坐番喺度睇其他兄弟比人打<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n7月2號監警會成立嘅專案組 只能&quot;審視警方在過去數場示威中的執法行動，並向特首提交報告。<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">然而，監警會沒有正式調查權，無法審視較高層的政治決定</span></strong></strong></span>&quot;<br />\n<br />\n所以!!! 希望大家可以focus番多D喺成立獨立調查會度!! <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">追究克警濫權問題!</span></span>"},{"pid":"61cf25af28ad66f42bece41753893fd8b93d415a","tid":1306202,"uid":278285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T05:29:36.000Z","msg":"sor 以為size 2 係大粒d字 點知仲細左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb7bb0e75f4f0b46c9fa42fcf28f8ce609f2d087","tid":1306202,"uid":278285,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T05:30:04.000Z","msg":"&quot;調查權方面，監警會主席梁定邦表示，警務處處長及特首承諾配合他們的工作，將提供所有需要的資料。然而，他同時承認，專案組沒有權力傳召證人或蒐集證據。可見，他們只能「審視」而非「調查」警隊行動；而最終監警會的報告能夠有多深入和全面，非常視乎警方提供多 少資料。<br />\n<br />\n由於警方正正是被審視的對象，換言之社會合理地認為，警方未必會主動且全面地交出資料。故此，此專案組未展開工作，已經陷入先天的認受性危機。即使報告在數個月後完成，能否獲得廣泛認同，實屬疑問。&quot;"},{"pid":"a7e2ca3f4e93e4aa79d206cb97cf845641fe512b","tid":1306202,"uid":278285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T05:30:39.000Z","msg":"(我無野講)"},{"pid":"e2d8d9b1781f16a0ca5e46f40572a470e9ff8ce6","tid":1306202,"uid":189151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T05:34:15.000Z","msg":"其實隻眼個制係preview<br />\n我無野講"},{"pid":"380e9825de42ada3944a3dfaf940820ee4d7e7ba","tid":1306202,"uid":278285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e2d8d9b1781f16a0ca5e46f40572a470e9ff8ce6","tid":1306202,"uid":189151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T05:34:15.000Z","msg":"其實隻眼個制係preview<br />\n我無野講"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T05:36:05.000Z","msg":"我太心急<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> thanks anyway!!!"},{"pid":"553509658851315f1f0fa005609ca8aada31f0a4","tid":1306202,"uid":260367,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T05:36:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9fd2814777817f37ac0ce3785b600c4d2bc8dca3","tid":1306202,"uid":189151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T05:37:33.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"0b6e07340af2840e2d445292cd101ee0060435b5","tid":1306202,"uid":278285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T05:38:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ybyaF2r.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FybyaF2r.png&h=571a6415&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"859928d12f625ae374609b65096c2229f5d46615","tid":1306202,"uid":277187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T05:39:54.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5abefd6cb2c031116039aa6a9c19364d67e42fd8","tid":1306202,"uid":278285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T05:46:12.000Z","msg":"Pushhhh"},{"pid":"672bd181ea4298b3fbe7486e65016e0c5976c4fb","tid":1306202,"uid":278285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T05:53:01.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;速龍小隊沒有編號，是警方刻意的政策；若然沒有合理解釋，這政策只會容讓警察避過責任。問題是，市民可以如何投訴？這已經不是個別警員涉嫌違規的問題，而是警隊在決策上可能出了錯，非現時的投訴機制可處理。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/01觀點/342764/為甚麼我們需要獨立委員會徹查612清場行動\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F01%E8%A7%80%E9%BB%9E%2F342764%2F%E7%82%BA%E7%94%9A%E9%BA%BC%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%E7%8D%A8%E7%AB%8B%E5%A7%94%E5%93%A1%E6%9C%83%E5%BE%B9%E6%9F%A5612%E6%B8%85%E5%A0%B4%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95&d=i5E3ds%2FeSPFE00WLmt852wmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=eea8b021\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/01觀點/342764/為甚麼我們需要獨立委員會徹查612清場行動</a>"}]}